| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4781 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0d7ba7a9-4ca6-5ca1-b018-6d6e38e85488"
